{"tid":2065895,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指報導親中「美國之音」正副主管同辭   班農班底接任","createTime":"2020-06-16T02:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T02:29:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ba839861a67d0b41f751dc5615b9ef9fadbd779f","tid":2065895,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:01:17.000Z","msg":"被指報導親中「美國之音」正副主管同辭 班農班底接任<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6996219/article-%e8%a2%ab%e6%8c%87%e5%a0%b1%e5%b0%8e%e8%a6%aa%e4%b8%ad%e3%80%8c%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e4%b9%8b%e9%9f%b3%e3%80%8d%e6%ad%a3%e5%89%af%e4%b8%bb%e7%ae%a1%e5%90%8c%e8%be%ad-%e7%8f%ad%e8%be%b2%e7%8f%ad%e5%ba%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6996219%2Farticle-%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258c%2587%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e5%25b0%258e%25e8%25a6%25aa%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e4%25b9%258b%25e9%259f%25b3%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e5%2589%25af%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e7%25ae%25a1%25e5%2590%258c%25e8%25be%25ad-%25e7%258f%25ad%25e8%25be%25b2%25e7%258f%25ad%25e5%25ba%2595%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7lwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=0f19c5ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6996219/article-%e8%a2%ab%e6%8c%87%e5%a0%b1%e5%b0%8e%e8%a6%aa%e4%b8%ad%e3%80%8c%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e4%b9%8b%e9%9f%b3%e3%80%8d%e6%ad%a3%e5%89%af%e4%b8%bb%e7%ae%a1%e5%90%8c%e8%be%ad-%e7%8f%ad%e8%be%b2%e7%8f%ad%e5%ba%95/</a><br />\n<br />\n「美國之音」(VOA)正副主管15日同時辭職，原因與川普政府不滿它新冠病毒報導「不公、親中、偏中」有關，接任者是曾為白宮前首席策略長巴農(Steve Bannon)班底的保守派製片人派克(Michael Pack)。<br />\n<br />\n阿曼達&middot;班奈特(Amanda Bennett)和副桑迪&middot;蘇加瓦拉(Sandy Sugawara)離職，正值VOA主管機構美國國際媒體署(U.S. Agency for Global Media)由川普盟友派克接掌，因為VOA有關中國處理新冠病毒危機的報導，與川普政府不同調。<br />\n<br />\n白宮對VOA不滿，不但發布聲明譴責，還吩咐聯邦疾病防治中心(CDC)勿與VOA記者合作。這對向來以客觀中立為傲的VOA，是非常罕見的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n班奈特和蘇加瓦拉在給同事的告別信中，稱讚VOA的員工，報導新冠病毒危機快速、果斷，希望新任主管不要干預新聞同仁執行法定任務。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨反對派克出任，原因之一是在國會聽證會上，他拒絕回答他過去生意往來的有關問題，不過，參院還是以53票對38票通過他的任命案。<br />\n<br />\n川普及圈內高官向來視VOA為「唱反調」的眼中釘，他們對VOA的敵視與不滿，4月9日爆發出來。那天，川普的新聞顧問史加維諾(Dan Scavino)在推特上，上傳一條VOA有關中國的報導，附加評語說，美國納稅人居然透過美國政府出錢經營的VOA，替中國宣傳，「好不丟臉！」<br />\n<br />\n那條VOA新聞，其實是美聯社的報導，內容是中國解除武漢封城。<br />\n<br />\n第二天，白宮發布新聞，指控VOA利用美國人民的納稅錢「替威權政權說話。」過幾天，川普加入撻伐，說VOA的報導「令人嫌惡」，參院必須趕快通過派克的任命案。<br />\n<br />\n班奈特是獲得普立茲獎的老牌記者，2016年起擔任VOA主管。她說，公營獨立媒體如VOA和政府控制的媒體，不同的地方是，「我們可以自由報導一個議題的各個面向，事實上，法律和VOA的成立章程，也規定我們必須這麼做。」"},{"pid":"34103e50951cbd35fedca25051c8917eaa04a406","tid":2065895,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"有得咁架咩"},{"pid":"bf7e3c8255f0ceab1754d38ac80472b390cf632a","tid":2065895,"uid":77277,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"班農接管<br />\n太好喇<br />\n<br />\n美國之音全面向右轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbdd44ae60e8e1e17b0f1e3cea1a39cba0bbae7","tid":2065895,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"出年拜登上台之後又換人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d93da8c49c3b77bedba5cf176bc7bee25cafe4","tid":2065895,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://smartbitchestrashybooks.com/WP/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/toast.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsmartbitchestrashybooks.com%2FWP%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Ftoast.gif&h=5cc4c70c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGood job, 滲透丫那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efa1017cc874dc37eafadaea67783708a7fc70b","tid":2065895,"uid":4783,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T02:04:21.000Z","msg":"客觀中立為傲的VOA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\